{"tid":1679854,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我地點解唔申請得禁制令？真心想知點解","createTime":"2019-10-28T12:19:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-29T08:38:00.000Z","uid":53673,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"65ead1b54fcdeff19c70baf83a0624bd002a4801","tid":1679854,"uid":53673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T12:19:35.000Z","msg":"自從泛民申請禁制令對付緊急法失敗之後<br />\n就再冇人幫市民申請禁制令<br />\n而對家就不斷申請 亦不斷獲批<br />\n我地禁唔到緊急法<br />\n起碼可以卑微少少禁制佢地既暴力掛？<br />\n朱經緯拿警棍揮到個人已經犯法要坐監<br />\n你申請禁扑頭呢d已犯法既野佢點會唔批呀？<br />\n好啦，最後都係冇人申請<br />\n咁不如你地話比我聽<br />\n點解我地唔可以申請？一定有原因！唔想成為歷史懸案/哲學問題"},{"pid":"10efdbfffc6b83df8a6f622b6c28a5949bebc068","tid":1679854,"uid":32577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T12:23:33.000Z","msg":"因為對面係謝賢"},{"pid":"883a876eb265b40dd989ca1b4ea35c0c4501c95d","tid":1679854,"uid":53673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"10efdbfffc6b83df8a6f622b6c28a5949bebc068","tid":1679854,"uid":32577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T12:23:33.000Z","msg":"因為對面係謝賢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T13:07:21.000Z","msg":"禁制令永遠由周家明審？"},{"pid":"1d95261350da7917913dd0f37655c06f0b68c5f2","tid":1679854,"uid":53673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T13:09:32.000Z","msg":"申請禁制令好貴？好花費人力物力？"},{"pid":"179c356fb83e3b8b92acaa0ea590d1acdfffa5ad","tid":1679854,"uid":53673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T13:16:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cf2c280eaf36a124a4857021f6041733a1801d78","tid":1679854,"uid":331830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T13:17:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"436f6c6878c7ea7794e6bdd2a4011643586fa63d","tid":1679854,"uid":41850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T13:18:35.000Z","msg":"人哋申請禁制令光速批核<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我哋申請禁制令又延遲又排期<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7